---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-(--color-text-secondary) mb-4">
        m87 CMS is an academic project developed by <strong>Miguel Benjamin Zubieta Rios</strong> as part of a software engineering course. The goal is to build a lightweight Flat File CMS that demonstrates modern web development practices.
      </p>
      <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) mb-4">
        For inquiries or contact: <a href="mailto:miguel.zubieta@proton.me" class="text-(--color-primary) hover:underline">miguel.zubieta@proton.me</a>
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What is a Flat CMS?</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        A Flat File CMS is a content management system that stores content as flat files (like Markdown) instead of using a database. This approach is simpler, faster, and perfect for small to medium-sized projects and static sites.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Key Features</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
        <li>Flat file-based content storage</li>
        <li>No database required</li>
        <li>Fast and lightweight</li>
        <li>Dark and light theme support</li>
        <li>Responsive and modern design</li>
        <li>Built with Astro, Tailwind CSS, and DaisyUI</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Technology Stack</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
        <li><strong>Astro:</strong> Static site generator for fast performance</li>
        <li><strong>Tailwind CSS:</strong> Utility-first CSS framework</li>
        <li><strong>DaisyUI:</strong> Component library built on Tailwind</li>
        <li><strong>Markdown:</strong> Flat file format for content</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
